::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_401090108-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401090108-->
::'''Liaison Officer William:''' It's all thanks to you &mdash; after hearing about your heroic deeds on the front lines, I've resolved to get myself out of this rut... It's time for a change.
